  The  purpose of btutils distribution is to support Baget 62-04 within specific
context.

  Instructions for installing the package.

  Before  installing make sure to have Baget 62-04 headers and bt23d-gcc in /bin
directory. Then execute following:
  ./configure --host=bt23d CFLAGS="-I*"
  make
  The * here is directory(ies) containing headers.
